    "title": "Marketplace Manager - FurnitureMart Holdings Services - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at FurnitureMart Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Marketplace Manager to strengthen our Chennai-based team.\n\nAbout FurnitureMart Holdings Services:\nFurnitureMart Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FurnitureMart Holdings Services!",
